{"tid":902241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人認同中国是適合帝制的?","createTime":"2018-11-14T16:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T17:10:04.000Z","uid":76310,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a77cbff4de0d59ee53143026c9bb3f5fdfb1005","tid":902241,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"有冇人認同中国是適合帝制的?<br />\n<br />\n我真心覺得中国是十分適合帝制<br />\n看見強国的官員, 百姓的想法根本和古代一模一樣, 民主公平自由平等根本是蠻夷洋鬼子的東西, 不合符中国的帝制和奴才制<br />\n大家認不認同?<br />\n<br />\n上訪事件=古時告御狀<br />\n国家主席南巡=皇帝出巡<br />\n貪官=古代貪官<br />\n忠君愛国=愛国愛黨<br />\n萬邦來朝=古代蠻夷訪京師<br />\n終身国家主席制=皇帝<br />\n黨天下=家天下"},{"pid":"146ac1afeb4840dda5378e8fdcbc52c8d3608a1b","tid":902241,"uid":22624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好想負皮"},{"pid":"84e69fb342fff55188c0d46563cb52ba303a164f","tid":902241,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:10:30.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"0c81cf81b828fd836638931c70c2c950ea55bef2","tid":902241,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"負皮"},{"pid":"b95ecbd8c826bc404072fb0e7a043dc7a6dfb13f","tid":902241,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔式邏輯反噬"},{"pid":"4215196737f058a531fcdf1995513ff3ac741236","tid":902241,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"此區域實行帝制:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/13/Region_of_xia.svg/728px-Region_of_xia.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F1%2F13%2FRegion_of_xia.svg%2F728px-Region_of_xia.svg.png&h=e47a24e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"451b2b20ea8dc2b04c28dab38963cefdd2a3c635","tid":902241,"uid":9962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"唔係中國適合帝制，而係現在所有教育、新聞